Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3, pulseaudio, systemd
Recommends: firewalld
Description: PulseAudio network audio server
 PulseAudio Network Server provides a reliable way to share audio from a
 PulseAudio-enabled system over the network. It includes automatic configuration
 management, health monitoring, and graceful error handling.
 .
 This package installs the server component that allows other systems to
 connect and receive audio streams over TCP.